citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:45 to 3:35 pm on
December 7th, 2023. Inspector phoned and left message at 2:45 pm and again at 3:06 pm. No one visible outdoors on
property. Waited at gate until 3:36 pm without a call back or appearance of licensee.
End Section
